Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 04 of Hand MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Osteonecrosis' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And a single selection localizer is enabled

When I click on the localizer
And I select 'Os lunatum' bone on the localizer
And I close the localizer
Then 'Stage I' radio button is enabled
And 'Stage II' radio button is enabled
And 'Stage III' radio button is enabled
And 'Stage IV' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Stage III' radio button
Then 'A' radio button is enabled
And 'B' radio button is enabled
And 'C' radio button is enabled
